name: Eva Dress
description:
This little dress is great for all seasons! Wear alone for those warm summer days, or double up with a sweater for autumn. Knot style bodice with adjustable ties. Also has a waist tie. Flower pin can be moved anywhere on the dress to your taste. Very versatile: can be worn with ties facing the front or ties facing the back! Includes elastic waist soft jersey leggings.

Dress is available in a size 2t.

Beautiful photography by Annmarie Walker!

"My soul rejoices in my God, for he has clothed me with garments of salvation." Isaiah 61:10

Spreading Joy-For every dress purchased from Felicity, one dress will be donated to a Little Dresses for Africa! Thanks for your support!
